message.content:
Fix the UI bug in splice-website/src/app/download/page.tsx.

The getFileExtension() function returns wrong extension:
```typescript
const getFileExtension = (download: DownloadOption) => {
  if (download.name.includes("UXP")) {
    return ".ccx";
  }
  return selectedOS === "mac" ? ".zxp" : ".exe";  // Bug: should be .pkg not .zxp
};
```

Fix to return ".pkg" for macOS since that's what the actual downloads are.

